explainers.AU Mic b: This planet orbits a young, active star with high energy output, resulting in a hot environment with an equilibrium temperature around 600 K. The star's youthful age contributes to increased stellar radiation, elevating the planet's temperature and influencing atmospheric conditions.

explainers.EPIC 220674823 c: This planet orbits a moderately warm star with an effective temperature of 5578 K.
